            <title>专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/778/732.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/778/732.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 12:50:02 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 6 月 30 日消息，水月雨近日在天猫上架一款“太空漫游探月版”&nbsp;TWS&nbsp;耳机定制“长征五号”礼盒，<strong>主要包含耳机本体 / 保护套 / 铭牌，售&nbsp;239&nbsp;元</strong>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1224" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/6afedaa1-4fff-4751-b4a7-6d89eaf23328.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="982" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="923" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/94e2ee07-6e37-4cb5-b3af-a998a0f7232d.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="830" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="653" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/3dbbba37-1b75-4497-ae20-ebd67e7e775f.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="940" /></p><p>据介绍，这款耳机拥有红色“长征五号”特别涂装，配备 13mm 动圈单元，采用镀钛球顶复合柔性悬边振膜，配备进口 CCAW 音圈和由 N52 钕磁体构建的磁路所组成的驱动系统。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="574" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/00569951-48b0-45f3-9d72-f98f7ac176fe.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="914" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="621" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/ab19f95d-dab2-4801-b651-34c00f6441fb.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="880" /></p><p>此外，该耳机支持&nbsp;35dB&nbsp;深度宽频&nbsp;ANC&nbsp;主动降噪，支持&nbsp;55ms&nbsp;低延迟游戏模式，同时支持通过手机&nbsp;App&nbsp;调节三档低音风格模式，同时拥有“专属友希探月语音”。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1195" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/413ebf87-bb4e-40c6-a5c8-d06eab44687b.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="878" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1219" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/fbe196d3-d483-42f9-88cb-57ec4ebe58ee.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="982" /></p><p>IT之家附耳机参数信息如下：</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="858" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/6/ffb6aef4-7dd6-4105-8e3f-1f09926de34a.png" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="804" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://s.click.taobao.com/t?e=m%3D2%26s%3DTiMGuIilyupw4vFB6t2Z2ueEDrYVVa64yK8Cckff7TVRAdhuF14FMcslUIcBZNz%2FMMgx22UI05ZKudquYbwz7QayRoXI2yHRcOEFtHWyuiQqGPuhWuerXg6KhLeHSnTd9CgRSquDwp8J865YvkC0DH24CV%2B0hMXd%2BYvtyi5RC3T9Umq014SDk1HQ59Ao%2BxITPOZWpAEiGVDAt060MWAtJ2sqf3xg2tfJbIph38OZ2%2BS7bUfskuhr8bWDO5VWjVh3QPDCOInGP4s4%2BfirBrx7mM7AMx9cWAx%2BlcdQbHRfePeEKIyknNpiew7HmpdDXzA1yaVr1QgMlnSiZ%2BQMlGz6FQ%3D%3D&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1719751748@21663780_136d_19069312a94_36e5@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i4/2212572610531/O1CN01XpIqu81FnFHDgwo4t_!!0-item_pic.jpg" title="专属友希语音，水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机“长征五号”礼盒 239 元开售" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name">水月雨“太空漫游探月版”TWS 耳机定制礼盒</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 239 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
